uding adrs it also analyzes various industries traded on exchanges around the world the firm offers proprietary and contrarian research which includes commentary on the stock market and the economy bond market observations equity strategies overall asset mix tactics and industryrelated subject matter it also uses proprietary databases for doing historical studies the firm seeks to identify equity leadership trends both domestically and globally it provides trend analysis using technical analysis the firm the leuthold group llc is a research firm it provides equity economic and fixed income research the firm universe includes securities traded on united states exchanges including adrs it also analyzes various industries traded on exchanges around the world the firm offers proprietary and contrarian research which includes commentary on the stock market and the economy bond market observations equity strategies overall asset mix tactics and industryrelated subject matter it also uses proprietary databases for doing historical studies the firm seeks to identify equity leadership trends both domestically and globally it provides trend analysis using technical analysis the firm models employ fundamental technical and quantitative factors it offers financial research broad sector industry group analysis and intrisic valuation studies the firm offers weekly monthly and quarterly reports it caters to institutional clients the firm was formerly known as the leuthold group and cross research the leuthold group llc was founded in  and is based in minneapolis minnesota detailed description  south sixth streetsuite minneapolis mn united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwleutholdgroupcom key executives for the leuthold group llc mr steven carlos leuthold founder and chairman mr ben mitchell managing director dr james william paulsen phd chief investment strategist mr douglas r ramsey cfa cmt chief investment officer mr matthew dudley managing editor compensation as of fiscal year 